.poster.avif?t=1773930950\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/1b9b31d85b65bd26962e54bfca4b6631.webm?t=1773930950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/1b9b31d85b65bd26962e54bfca4b6631.mp4?t=1773930950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A WORLD WITH HISTORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore silent Sanctuary docks, Refuel Outposts, Underwater cities, and long-forgotten Seed Vaults. The story is uncovered through places, logs, memories, and the remains of a civilization that tried to outlive its own world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/61a6405bfbd42f798bd439d571c76cbf.poster.avif?t=1773930950\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/61a6405bfbd42f798bd439d571c76cbf.webm?t=1773930950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/61a6405bfbd42f798bd439d571c76cbf.mp4?t=1773930950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
